AB  - The malfunction and failure of the metal structure of cranes often cause serious safety accidents. Today, the management of the port crane group is still in the stage of routine inspection, regular inspection and maintenance of equipment health according to the plan in China, and there will be safety hazards such as maintenance and repair not in time. Aiming at the metal structure health monitoring and daily management of port crane group, this paper designs a comprehensive management pre-warning system based on condition monitoring, considering the enterprise demand, system practicability and scalability, and realizes the combination of static detection model and dynamic real-time monitoring model. With the application of the system, port security and management efficiency can be comprehensively improved, and the facility foundation and data foundation can be provided for the construction of "smart port".
