AB  - As the core component of a ship, Marine equipment has a wide variety of types, complex internal structure and working principle, so it is inconvenient to learn large-scale Marine equipment, so the research of Marine equipment information model is proposed. The three-dimensional information model of the turbine equipment is constructed and the simulation experiment is carried out, so that the structure, operation principle and other information of the equipment can be easily and intuitively understood. The three phase squirrel-cage asynchronous motor is studied as an example, and its information model is created, including: building a 3D model in Rhino modeling software; Import Unity3D for virtual disassembly and electrical characteristics simulation; Use My SQL database to store, query and modify model data. Finally, the development of Marine equipment information model is realized, which provides guidance and practical significance for the exploration of informatization, virtualization and digitalization in the Marine industry.
